text: Weekend () is a 1967 French Italian black comedy movie directed by Jean-Luc Godard and starring Mireille Darc, Jean Yanne, Yves Afonso, Juliet Berto, Paul Gégauff, Jean-Pierre Léaud. It was distributed by Athos Films. ==Other websites== * Category:1967 comedy movies Category:1960s black comedy movies Category:1960s road movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Italian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Jean-Luc Godard Category:Dystopian movies Category:Movies about cannibalism
